\paragraph{Survey Composition}
Each participant was asked to estimate the area of a marked region of 18 plots (details below). For each estimation, participants had to answer within 25 seconds before the survey automatically advanced to the next question. This ensured that individuals did not measure sections of the plot or otherwise calculate their answers.

